Fine tuning the model.

Fine tuning means: Training the model on specific Task. Here in
auto completion case, we are going to train on specific task of auto 
completion 
We retain the base training knowledge what it has during the pre training 
stage 

How we fine tune?
We use the data set of 1 billion email messages for training on auto completion 
task 

ML Objective and loss function 

ML Objective and loss function remain same,i.e., we use next token prediction 
as the ML task and cross entropy is the loss function 
But only difference is loss is calculated based on email data 

How we train on auto completion task?

We give email body and also email subject recipents and previous email 
conversations as part of email training 
We take billions of different such emails and fine tune on the task. 
Why email body is not only sufficient?
because some email don't have any body they just have receipient name
For i am sending mail to john, then once i type Dear... it should 
suggest next token "John", thats possible only if we consider subect 
recepient email details and old mails 

